<title>currentColor is inherited correctly in prophoto-rgb RCS</title><title>
</title><link rel="help" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-5/#resolving-rcs">
<link rel="author" href="mailto:chris@w3.org" title="Chris Lilley">
<style>
div {
  width: 99px;
  height: 101px;
  background-color: red;
  color: red;
  background-color: color(from currentColor prophoto-rgb r g b);
}
div div {
  color: green;
  background-color: inherit;
}
</style>
